title: The Gavin McInnes Show 2016-01-21 Episode 81 Chuck C. Johnson

The always outspoken and "controversial" Gavin McInnes joins the Anthony Cumia Network - with new shows twice a week. In addition to co-founding VICE, the author, actor, podcast host, and political pundit is at the forefront of the modern "anti-PC" movement and a perfect match for the cutting edge and newly emerging ACN.

Guests: Chris Cotton, Chuck C. Johnson, Pax Dickinson

Episode 81: Today on TGMS, Gavin talks about Hasidic Jews jizzing on his windshield. Chuck Johnson and Pax Dickinson talk about getting fired from their jobs and removed from Twitter. They talk about Amy Schumer's joke controversy. Chris Cotton joins to talk about socialism.
